li></ul><p class="sc-fmBCVi laenLa pf-52_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-54_">Our founders actively participate in all stages of our work and are present daily in our production studio, looking for ways to improve and working hand in hand with our workers.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-kLwhqv julQCc pf-55_"><button type="button" class="sc-giYglK gvnqsv pf-56_ pf-anchor" data-header-id="a5078910-9f30-432f-9599-fc7dfac75588" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Wages</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="a5078910-9f30-432f-9599-fc7dfac75588" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-ezbkAF ikwrMb pf-58_"><div class="sc-hiCibw hHrFfF pf-59_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-hAcGzb bAQARH pf-60_"><p class="sc-fmBCVi laenLa pf-61_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-63_">We provide our workers with waves that are above the minimum wage standard in Peru. We aim to reward them with more benefits as soon as we become profitable.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-kLwhqv julQCc pf-64_"><button type="button" class="sc-giYglK gvnqsv pf-65_ pf-anchor" data-header-id="c054bdd4-2c72-4d8a-ad43-2ebf16c215f6" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Gender Equality & Empowerment</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="c054bdd4-2c72-4d8a-ad43-2ebf16c215f6" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-ezbkAF ikwrMb pf-67_"><div class="sc-hiCibw hHrFfF pf-68_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-hAcGzb bAQARH pf-69_"><p class="sc-fmBCVi laenLa pf-70_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-72_">At AYA, we accept workers of all genders. Our company consists of our founders, marketing team, art team, assistants, accountants and production workers. As of May 2022, we have 36 employees and freelancers working with us, 27 of whom are women.</span></p><p class="sc-fmBCVi laenLa pf-73_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-75_">Everyone at AYA can use their voice freely to disclose their opinions and ideas. They have a high level of autonomy in their day-to-day activities.&nbsp;</span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-kLwhqv julQCc pf-76_"><button type="button" class="sc-giYglK gvnqsv pf-77_ pf-anchor" data-header-id="7dfac755-88af-46a1-9369-fc408f343a59" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Racial Justice</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="7dfac755-88af-46a1-9369-fc408f343a59" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-ezbkAF ikwrMb pf-79_"><div class="sc-hiCibw hHrFfF pf-80_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-hAcGzb bAQARH pf-81_"><p class="sc-fmBCVi laenLa pf-82_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-84_">AYA is an inclusive brand which is why nobody is discriminated for their nationality or color. We are proud to be working with diverse people. Our employees and freelancers are from Peru, Venezuela, United States, Spain and the Czech Republic.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-9fb8" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-bQtKYq fbyRgD pf-120_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-jHkVzv dyVEVs"><div 