g about us could compromise the future of our business.&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p class="sc-fmBCVi laenLa pf-94_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-96_">We take responsiblity for our impact across the whole product lifecycle: impact on the environment, people and animals. We make sure that each stage of our supply chain, from raw materials to product disposal, have minimal impact.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-cbb3" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-bQtKYq fbyRgD pf-97_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-jHkVzv dyVEVs"><div class="sc-hiCibw hHrFfF pf-98_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-hAcGzb bAQARH pf-99_"><h2 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-ctqQKy ldqOxu pf-100_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-102_">Animal Rights</span></h2><p class="sc-fmBCVi laenLa pf-103_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-105_">The only material of an animal origin is Royal Alpaca Wool, sourced from small Peruvian co-op farmers who own the maximum of 200 alpacas per farm. All alpacas are non-mulesed, receive regular medical care, and roam free in the highlands.</span></p><p class="sc-fmBCVi laenLa pf-106_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-108_">We do not use any fur, leather, down/feathers, angora, and exotic animal hairs and skins.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><script>window.__pagefly_setting__={"baseURL":"https://apps.pagefly.io","analyticsURL":"https://analytics.pagefly.io","isBackend":false,"cdnURL":"https://cdn.pagefly.io","pageflyVersion":"3.17.17","shopDomain":"ayaecofashion.myshopify.com","elementData":{},"pageTitle":"Ethics","pageType":"page","pageId":"e94994ba-5816-4bb0-80c7-9dabff598f91","lazyLoad":false,"forceByPassGoogleLightHouse":false